===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|form||}}

[[Transitive]]:
# To [[shape]].
# To construct or [[frame]].
#* The ideas and [[opinion]]s we '''form''' in early life remain with us.
# To [[contract]] or create.
#* We '''formed''' many friendships at band camp.
# To instruct, almost indoctrinate
#* To form a pupil

[[Intransitive]]:
# To take or [[assume]] a [[shape]].

